<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Day-After Brunch</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-brunch">
    <div class="hero-overlay-brunch"></div>
    <div class="hero-content-brunch">
      <h1>Day-After Brunch</h1>
      <p>A relaxed and heartfelt gathering to reflect, laugh, and bond with your loved ones after the big day.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="content-brunch">
    <div class="section-brunch two-columns-brunch refined-brunch-brunch reverse-brunch">
      <div class="text-brunch">
        <h2>Why Host a Brunch?</h2>
        <p>
          The day-after brunch is a beautiful way to wind down your wedding festivities. It's casual yet elegant, and gives you more time to connect with out-of-town guests and share stories from the big day. Think of it as a joyful send-off that leaves everyone with a warm memory.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image-brunch image-wrapper-brunch">
        <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/e1/2a/7e/e12a7e6e793e44689e0418354a108e8a.jpg" alt="Brunch Table Setup">
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What to Include -->
    <div class="section-brunch two-columns-brunch reverse-brunch">
      <div class="image-brunch">
        <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/c0/34/10/c034104cbc24c23555c8a4c371fe7fa7.jpg" alt="Relaxed Dining Space">
      </div>
      <div class="text-brunch">
        <h2>What to Include</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Delicious breakfast & brunch spread</li>
          <li>Fresh juices, mimosas, or a coffee bar</li>
          <li>Relaxing playlist or light background music</li>
          <li>Casual seating and minimal décor with floral touches</li>
          <li>Printed thank-you cards or photo slideshows</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Planning section button-->
    <div class="section-brunch luxury-cta-brunch">
      <div class="cta-content-brunch">
        <h2>Plan Effortlessly With Us</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're hosting in a charming backyard, a rooftop venue, or an exclusive estate, we craft unforgettable brunch experiences tailored to your style. Let us take care of every detail — from curated menus and floral centerpieces to serene ambiance and guest comfort.
        </p>
        <a href="/planning" class="btn-brunch luxury-btn-brunch">Start Planning</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>